           MOVE  ZEROS  TO  CNDTACUM-MOVDEB(X).
           MOVE  ZEROS  TO  CNDTACUM-MOVCRE(X).
           MOVE  ZEROS  TO  CNDTACUM-SALDO(X).
       F-ZEROS.

